      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-prior-studies-synthesis",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Synthesis of prior CFD hemolysis validation studies (2015–2023)",
      "description": "A comprehensive synthesis of multiple prior independent validation studies examining CFD-based hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps, including the Bludszuweit (1995) power-law model, the Garon-Farinas (2004) accumulated damage model, and five subsequent benchmark exercises conducted under FDA Critical Path Initiative guidance. This synthesis aggregates quantitative error metrics, turbulence model sensitivity findings, and mesh resolution recommendations from across the literature, providing a consolidated evidentiary basis for the modeling choices adopted in the present COU. The breadth of coverage and consistency of conclusions across independent groups substantially strengthens confidence in the selected model form and numerical parameters.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cpb-hemolysis-worst-case"
    }
  ],
